OL,3,CBoy, 13, dies after crash on M4
OL,5,FA 13-year-old boy has died following a
OL,6,Fcrash between a car and a van on the
OL,7,FM4 near Swindon.
OL,9,FThe collision happened between
OL,10,Fjunctions 16 for Swindon and 17 for
OL,11,FChippenham at around 8pm yesterday
OL,12,Fevening (Saturday, 18 July).
OL,14,FA woman who was in the same car as the
OL,15,Fteenager was taken to hospital with
OL,16,Fserious injuries, Wiltshire Police
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FThe force said the drivers of both
OL,20,Fvehicles were not seriously injured.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
