OL,3,CBoy, 13, dies after crash on M4
OL,5,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,6,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,7,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,8,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,10,FThe M4 westbound carriageway between
OL,11,Fjunctions 16 and 17 shut for around 14
OL,12,Fhours while investigations took place.
OL,14,FWiltshire Police is appealing for
OL,15,Fwitnesses to come forward.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the force said:
OL,18,F"Our thoughts are with the family of
OL,19,Fthe teenager at this incredibly
OL,20,Fdifficult time and we ask that their
OL,21,Fprivacy is respected.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
